data.description: Price improved! No flooding here! Where fine architecture meets marine lovers! Nestled on an oversized lot and positioned on the canal with a unique panorama-like view, that will not disappoint. As you walk in, you are greeted by the blissful views of the Gulf and a modern open floor plan with the kitchen island being your stage. Top rated granite counter tops throughout, luxury cabinetry and ceilings that seem to touch the sky are what stands out with your first steps. This home is a 3 bedroom with a den/office and 2 full bathrooms. The master ensuit impresses with a large granite double-sink countertop and custom shower. As you make your way outside to your oasis, you walk out to a large screened in lanai that hosts your own personal spa (hot tub), which makes evenings even more special when soaking in the views. Marine lovers will not be disappointed with having your own 10,000 lb boat lift and dock. Your short trip to gulf access is not interrupted by any bridges so having a sail boat would be a breeze. The property being almost a double lot, positioned on a corner, and spectacular one of a kind canal views is a unique opportunity which one must see for themselves in person. I have a pool estimate on file.. A Home Warranty is offered for this home!
